dalserver.conf

Class NTFITSHeaderKeywords

  • java.lang.Object
    • dalserver.conf.FITSHeaderKeywords
      • dalserver.conf.NTFITSHeaderKeywords

  • public class NTFITSHeaderKeywords
extends FITSHeaderKeywords
    a FITSHeaderKeywords container implemented on top of the nom.tam.fits.Header class. It is expected that a nom.tam.fits-based FITS reader will populated this container by calling the addHeader(Header) function for each HDU in the file and in the order that they appear in the file.
